\left(\left(c_{1}, \ldots, c_{2}\right) \mapsto \left\{\left(\sum_{l \in \mathbb{Z}}~\left(l + 1\right) \cdot c_{1} \cdot \ldots \cdot c_{2}\right) = \sum_{l \in \mathbb{Z}}~\left(\left(l + 1\right) \cdot c_{1} \cdot \ldots \cdot c_{2}\right) \textrm{ if } \left(c_{1} \in \mathbb{C}\right) \land \ldots \land \left(c_{2} \in \mathbb{C}\right)\right..\right)